#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.swaplevel.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.swaplevel"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:1 of
msgid "Swap levels i and j in a :class:`MultiIndex`."
msgstr "在 :class:`MultiIndex` 中交换层级 i 和 j。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:3 of
msgid "Default is to swap the two innermost levels of the index."
msgstr "默认交换索引的两个最内层。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:5
#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:7 of
msgid "Levels of the indices to be swapped. Can pass level name as string."
msgstr "要交换的索引层级。可以传递层级名称作为字符串。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:9 of
msgid ""
"The axis to swap levels on. 0 or 'index' for row-wise, 1 or 'columns' for"
" column-wise."
msgstr "交换层级的轴。0 或 'index' 表示行方向，1 或 'columns' 表示列方向。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:13 of
msgid "DataFrame with levels swapped in MultiIndex."
msgstr "在 MultiIndex 中交换层级后的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:17 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:34 of
msgid ""
"In the following example, we will swap the levels of the indices. Here, "
"we will swap the levels column-wise, but levels can be swapped row-wise "
"in a similar manner. Note that column-wise is the default behaviour. By "
"not supplying any arguments for i and j, we swap the last and second to "
"last indices."
msgstr ""
"在以下示例中，我们将交换索引的层级。这里我们按列方向交换层级，但也可以"
"按行方向进行类似操作。注意列方向是默认行为。如果不为 i 和 j 提供任何参数"
"，则交换最后两个层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:47 of
msgid ""
"By supplying one argument, we can choose which index to swap the last "
"index with. We can for example swap the first index with the last one as "
"follows."
msgstr ""
"通过提供一个参数，我们可以选择将最后一个索引与哪个索引交换。例如，我们"
"可以按如下方式将第一个索引与最后一个交换。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.swaplevel.df_swaplevel:58 of
msgid ""
"We can also define explicitly which indices we want to swap by supplying "
"values for both i and j. Here, we for example swap the first and second "
"indices."
msgstr ""
"我们还可以通过为 i 和 j 提供值来明确定义要交换的索引。例如，这里我们交换"
"第一个和第二个索引。"

